title: Ground News - Israel is losing weapons to Hamas, withdrawing battalions. Gaza war now becomes Stalingrad
text:
Summary by Ground News Pakistan Air Force is the reason I was spanked during the dark hours of a December morning in Jodhpur. The sound of the aircraft screaming through the night, the flashes of anti-aircraft fire, the brilliance of the bombs going off followed by their thudding sounds was all too electrifying to experience it from the womb of a bomb shelter.
